Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.49,0:00:06.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,聊天结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.40,0:00:10.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,到了切蛋糕的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:13.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,快  把小孩交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:15.91,somari text,,0,0,0,,迫不得已了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.57,0:00:19.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,我不会把索玛丽交出去…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.92,0:00:27.96,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.17,0:00:29.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.67,0:00:31.76,somari text,,0,0,0,,快醒来  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.55,0:00:35.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要  放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.88,0:00:36.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:39.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:41.01,somari title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1556.533,1061.467)}\N{\fade(1000,850)\blur6\pos(1502.133,1058.267)}心心相连的父女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.44,0:00:44.52,somari text,,0,0,0,,这么纤细的脖子  一下就能切开
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:47.94,somari text,,0,0,0,,那怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:09.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,那家伙  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:12.30,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.26,0:01:20.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.69,0:01:30.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,目标坐标确认
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.86,0:01:34.99,somari text,,0,0,0,,体内热量以及内心限制变更开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:41.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:45.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,发动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:01:59.02,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:29.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,怪…怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:30.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.58,0:02:33.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:37.42,somari text,,0,0,0,,等…等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:52.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:54.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,走吧  得阻止他才行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.19,0:03:02.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,我可没听说是这么危险的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:06.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,我也不知道哥雷姆这么危险
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:17.30,somari text,,0,0,0,,目标确认
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:19.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,歼灭开始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:32.02,somari text,,0,0,0,,目标确认
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.64,0:03:34.23,somari text,,0,0,0,,饶…饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:37.15,somari text,,0,0,0,,是我错了  是我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:39.07,somari text,,0,0,0,,不行  哥雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:44.99,somari text,,0,0,0,,亚巴希
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:50.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:53.58,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎么变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:03:58.88,somari text,,0,0,0,,你这样可不能让她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:01.80,somari text,,0,0,0,,不能让你所珍重的人看见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:08.01,somari text,,0,0,0,,亚巴希
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:14.02,somari text,,0,0,0,,歼灭目标
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:20.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:21.99,somari text,,0,0,0,,不行  快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:23.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要  我不走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:27.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,我不想爸爸伤害到谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:32.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:33.37,somari text,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:36.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,因为  爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:41.30,somari text,,0,0,0,,一直都会抚摸我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:00.98,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:03.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:19.96,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.29,0:05:23.99,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:37.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:40.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:49.66,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:52.66,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  爸爸  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:05:57.58,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:01.92,somari text,,0,0,0,,太好了  你醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:04.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,你一直躺着不动我们可担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:08.30,somari text,,0,0,0,,我  到底
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:12.47,somari text,,0,0,0,,什么啊  闹得那么大你一点都不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:15.42,somari text,,0,0,0,,只有些许断片的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:18.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,你的伤是我造成的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:20.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.35,0:06:24.57,somari text,,0,0,0,,不过这种程度比起你不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:26.50,somari text,,0,0,0,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:30.82,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  手臂治不好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.36,0:06:31.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:34.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,不会痛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:35.91,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:41.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,抱歉让你担心了  索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:42.75,somari text,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:47.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:48.80,somari text,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:50.30,somari text,,0,0,0,,手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:04.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:23.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,左腕以及23%表皮缺损
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:26.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,燃失一部分体液
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:31.17,somari text,,0,0,0,,日常活动限制到76%
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:33.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,剩下的时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:42.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,剩下的时间  不明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:49.99,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽  跑到你那边了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:51.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,好  交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:57.12,somari text,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:07:58.58,somari text,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:01.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,不要太勉强  你才大病初愈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:03.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:05.04,somari text,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:09.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,虽然有些许不便  不过很快能习惯这个身体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:12.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  亚巴希
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:14.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,我们抓到了好多鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:17.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,好  挺厉害的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:24.27,somari text,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:31.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,喂喂  别吃那么急嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:34.65,somari text,,0,0,0,,因为好好吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:35.91,somari text,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:40.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽有在食物前过度兴奋的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:45.04,somari text,,0,0,0,,虽然我平时有让她吃慢点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:49.59,somari text,,0,0,0,,说完就噎住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:53.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,好了快喝水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.29,0:08:58.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:01.10,somari text,,0,0,0,,是你吃太急了才会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:03.39,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯  我以后会注意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:20.49,somari text,,0,0,0,,锡佐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:28.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,是吗  你注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:29.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:37.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,那么  你现在的身体是什么状况
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:41.18,somari text,,0,0,0,,自那个时候以来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:43.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,加上体内组织的损坏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:47.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,视觉以及听觉都有状况不佳的情况发生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:50.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,需要限制的行动也增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:56.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,这样下去  我终将会停止活动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:09:58.49,somari text,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:02.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,不过  应该还有什么是你能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:05.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,因为你还有时间对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:08.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,不明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:14.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,那一天  离开森林后与众多的命运抗争的我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:18.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,决定于索玛丽共同前进
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:21.97,somari text,,0,0,0,,不过  也有无法违抗的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:26.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,因此我决定从索玛丽身边…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.64,0:10:30.65,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:33.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,无论你做出什么选择
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:36.61,somari text,,0,0,0,,我都决定帮助你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.69,0:10:39.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,这就是约定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:44.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,不过如果可以的话我希望你再考虑一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:51.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,这对你和索玛丽来说真的是最好的选择吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:15.57,somari text,,0,0,0,,看得到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.07,0:11:23.57,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽  把风帽往下戴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:37.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,感觉好热闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:45.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临  小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:48.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  看上去全都好好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:51.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,看上去好像是在庆祝节日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.14,0:11:54.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆啊  真是难得一见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:56.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,你们是旅人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:11:59.61,somari text,,0,0,0,,欢迎参加本村的丰收节
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:02.57,somari text,,0,0,0,,已经到这个时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:04.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,丰收节？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:08.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,这是一个感谢先祖们为我们带来作物丰收的节日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:12.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,这就是节日吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:15.67,somari text,,0,0,0,,大家好像都拿着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:18.75,somari text,,0,0,0,,那是乘风花
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:20.59,somari text,,0,0,0,,乘风花？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:24.55,somari text,,0,0,0,,用于迎接先祖们灵魂的回归
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.13,0:12:26.30,somari text,,0,0,0,,灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:29.31,somari text,,0,0,0,,说简单点就是鬼怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:32.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽害怕鬼怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:35.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,鬼怪其实不可怕的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.27,0:12:38.23,somari text,,0,0,0,,那是先祖们的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:42.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,是我们重要的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:44.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,你瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:47.03,somari text,,0,0,0,,风起的正好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.45,0:12:55.75,somari text,,0,0,0,,像那样放飞乘风花
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:57.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,那光芒将会成为信标
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.45,0:13:03.30,somari text,,0,0,0,,指引已去世父母的灵魂回到我们的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:05.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:07.64,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:09.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:12.97,somari text,,0,0,0,,所有生物死后都将回归大地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:16.73,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以灵魂和鬼怪并不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:19.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,这是自然之理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:21.27,somari text,,0,0,0,,是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:24.07,somari text,,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:26.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎么了  七仔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:29.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,去买玩具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:31.49,somari text - top,,0,0,0,,快点  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:32.95,somari text,,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法  今天就特许一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:35.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,孙子的央求总是拒绝不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:37.04,somari text,,0,0,0,,选哪一个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:43.50,somari text,,0,0,0,,在不久的将来  我们也将迎来「回归」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:46.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,但是啊  哥雷姆先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:48.55,somari text,,0,0,0,,大家都深信着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:58.33,somari text,,0,0,0,,死并不是一切的结束  死后会化作灵魂回到自己重要的人身边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:05.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,那种东西只不过是无意义的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:13.53,somari text,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:18.04,somari text,,0,0,0,,看上去好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:20.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,店主  请给我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:21.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:22.17,somari text,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:24.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,平时一直都叮嘱我不要吃太多零食
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:28.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,因为是节日  今天就特许一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:30.64,somari text,,0,0,0,,节日好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:35.97,somari text,,0,0,0,,除此之外还有什么想要的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:37.98,somari text,,0,0,0,,肉还是糖果
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:42.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:45.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸保护过度了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:47.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:48.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:51.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,看上去吃得好香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:54.70,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸给我买的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:15:00.50,somari text,,0,0,0,,但要是吃这么多甜食可是会得蛀牙的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:05.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,好像什么开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:11.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,哇  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:16.64,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:21.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,能看见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:24.11,somari text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  亚巴希
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:26.73,somari text,,0,0,0,,亚巴希  我也要  我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:29.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,笨蛋  你都成年了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:30.65,somari text,,0,0,0,,切  小气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.79,0:15:34.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,哇  好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:15:58.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,好开心啊  爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:15:59.10,somari text,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:00.22,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:03.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:13.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,按他那个身形  也不会迷路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:18.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆  这就是你的选择吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:21.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:25.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,恐怕  哥雷姆不会再回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:28.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,你这什么玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:29.88,somari text,,0,0,0,,一点都不好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:31.88,somari text,,0,0,0,,他其实一直在苦恼着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:34.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,应该怎么面对自己剩下的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:37.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,就算这样他怎么可能丢下小姑娘自己消失不见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:40.10,somari text,,0,0,0,,我劝过他了的  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:46.52,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  爸爸  爸爸  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:15.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:53.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:55.59,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:17:57.80,somari text,,0,0,0,,停住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:01.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,禁止你继续接近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:03.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.77,0:18:08.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,我无法再和索玛丽一起踏上旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:11.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:14.07,somari text,,0,0,0,,是因为索玛丽吃了太多甜食吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:15.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:19.95,somari text,,0,0,0,,还是因为索玛丽总是不听话一个人跑去玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:20.99,somari text,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:25.91,somari text,,0,0,0,,那是讨厌索玛丽了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.45,0:18:27.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,并不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:29.12,somari text,,0,0,0,,那为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.08,0:18:35.59,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  不要这样  索玛丽不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:38.26,somari text,,0,0,0,,你答应过的  答应过的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:39.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,和我一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:42.89,somari text - top,,0,0,0,,爸爸  你听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.29,0:18:42.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽  放手  索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:45.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸要和索玛丽一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:48.52,somari text,,0,0,0,,一直一直  哪怕是旅途结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.93,0:18:51.70,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽长大了  也要一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:52.98,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:06.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,如果我再次失去控制的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.76,0:19:10.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,我会让索玛丽陷入危险中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:14.59,somari text,,0,0,0,,因为  在这里分开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:16.92,somari text,,0,0,0,,才是为了索玛丽的幸福着想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:20.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,才不是  爸爸一点都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.88,0:19:27.26,somari text,,0,0,0,,要是爸爸不在了  索玛丽会很寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:31.06,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸不会寂寞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:33.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆没有感情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:35.94,somari text,,0,0,0,,有的  有的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:41.66,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸总是因为索玛丽转眼间就不知到跑哪去了很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:48.37,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸总是因为索玛丽会不会感冒和受伤而感到担心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:54.96,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸虽然有时候会很严厉  但那是为了不让我做危险的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:20:02.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸总是在我睡觉的时候陪伴在我身边  那是为了不让我感到寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.70,0:20:11.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸总是牵着我的手  那是为了能够让索玛丽和自己一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:19.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:22.61,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:29.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,因为爸爸是索玛丽的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:35.33,somari text,,0,0,0,,我也有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:37.59,somari text,,0,0,0,,感情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:40.17,somari text,,0,0,0,,心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:43.80,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.39,0:20:48.26,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:53.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:56.52,somari text,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:08.37,somari text,,0,0,0,,我想要和索玛丽在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:11.16,somari text,,0,0,0,,作为索玛丽的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:16.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,哪怕是要和这个世界的一切做斗争
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:22.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:27.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,这就是我唯一的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.76,0:21:29.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,索玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.64,0:21:41.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,要一直一直在一起哦  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:45.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯  一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.45,0:21:56.96,somari text,,0,0,0,,哪怕是一分钟一秒  也想要时间再长一些
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.25,0:22:00.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,即使是化为灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.63,0:22:02.59,somari text,,0,0,0,,也要永远和你
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,——————ED——————
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.85,0:22:26.11,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}並ぶ影の大きさ比べ笑う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.85,0:22:26.11,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}比较着并排的影子相视而笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.49,0:22:29.68,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}夕暮れを背に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.49,0:22:29.68,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}把夕阳甩在身后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.08,0:22:40.75,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}そっと風に乗せたのは　まだ小さな願い事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.08,0:22:40.75,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}乘风而去的是那小小的祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.19,0:22:47.78,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}永遠とか　生命だとか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.19,0:22:47.78,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}什么是永远  什么是生命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.10,0:22:52.38,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}何も分からずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.10,0:22:52.38,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}我还一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.85,0:23:04.66,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}真っ直ぐな瞳で　見上げた横顔は眩しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.85,0:23:04.66,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}只知道当我抬头仰望你时  你的侧脸总是那么地闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.62,0:23:11.01,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}重ねた手に伝う温もりは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.62,0:23:11.01,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}手牵着手传递的这份温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.51,0:23:15.53,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}どんなときも愛をくれたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.51,0:23:15.53,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}无论何时都在给予我爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.91,0:23:21.42,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}溢れ出すこの想いが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.91,0:23:21.42,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}这不断溢出的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.75,0:23:27.19,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}あなたに届く日まで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.75,0:23:27.19,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}直到传达到给你的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.59,0:23:35.74,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}交わした約束進もう  未来へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.59,0:23:35.74,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}向着共同许下的诺言和未来  前进吧
